\c 29
\s Dhavhidhi anodzingwa neVaFirisitia pakurwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino VaFirisitia vakaunganidza hondo dzavo dzose\x + 28.1.\x* paAfeki\x + Josh. 12.18.\x*, asi VaIsraeri vakavaka musasa patsime\x + Vato. 7.1. Vato. 6.33.\x* riri paJezireeri\x + 29.11. 30.1. Josh. 17.16. Josh. 15.56.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino madzishe eVaFirisitia aipfuura akaita mazana mazana uye zvuru zvuru\x + Josh. 13.3.\x*, naDhavhidhi nevarume vake vaipfuura shure naAkishi\x + 28.1,2.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino machinda eVaFirisitia akati: VaHebheru ava chii? Akishi ndokuti kumachinda eVaFirisitia: Uyu haasi Dhavhidhi, muranda waSauro mambo waIsraeri, wanga aneni mazuva ano kana makore ano here\x + 27.7.\x*? Uye handina kuwana chinhu kwaari\x + 29.6. 25.28. Dhan. 6.5.\x* kubva pazuva rekuwa kwake kusvika nhasi\x + Gen.. 25.18.\x*.
\v 4 Asi machinda eVaFirisitia akamutsamwira; machinda eVaFirisitia ndokuti kwaari: Dzosera munhu uyu adzokere kunzvimbo yake kwawakamuisa\x + 29.11. 27.6. 30.1.\x*, uye ngaarege kuburuka pamwe nesu kuhondo, kuti asava muvengi wedu muhondo. Nokuti uyu angazviita anodiwa sei kuna ishe wake? Hazvisi nemisoro yevanhu ava here\x + 14.21.\x*?
\v 5 Uyu haasi Dhavhidhi wavaibvumirana pamusoro pake mukutamba vachiti: Sauro wakauraya zvuru zvake, asi Dhavhidhi makumi ezvuru ake\x + 18.7. 21.11. Vato. 21.21.\x*?
\p
\v 6 Zvino Akishi wakadana Dhavhidhi ndokuti kwaari: \add Na\add*Jehovha mupenyu, zvirokwazvo iwe wakarurama\x + Rut. 3.13.\x*, nekubuda kwako nekupinda kwako neni mumusasa kwakanaka pameso angu\x + 2 Madz. 19.27. Isa. 37.28. 2 Sam. 3.25. Eze. 43.11.\x*, nokuti handina kuwana chakaipa kwauri kubva pazuva rawakasvika kwandiri kusvika zuva rino\x + 29.3.\x*; asi hauna kunaka pameso emadzishe\x + Josh. 13.3.\x*.
\v 7 Naizvozvo ikozvino dzokera ugoenda nerugare\x + 1.17.\x*, kuti urege kuita chakaipa pameso emadzishe eVaFirisitia\x + Josh. 13.3.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakati kuna Akishi: Asi ndaitei? Uye makawanei kumuranda wenyu kubva pazuva randakava pamberi penyu kusvika nhasi, kuti handingaendi ndigonorwa nevavengi vashe wangu mambo?
\v 9 Zvino Akishi wakapindura ndokuti kuna Dhavhidhi: Ndakaziva kuti wakanaka pameso angu semutumwa waMwari\x + 2 Sam. 14.17,20. 19.27.\x*; koga machinda eVaFirisitia ati: Haangakwiri nesu kuhondo\x + 29.4.\x*.
\v 10 Naizvozvo zvino chimuka mangwanani-ngwanani pamwe nevaranda vashe wako vakauya newe; zvino kana mamuka mangwanani-ngwanani kwachena kwamuri, muende\x + 29.4. 1 Makor. 12.19-22.\x*.
\v 11 Naizvozvo Dhavhidhi wakamuka mangwanani, iye nevanhu vake, kuenda mangwanani, kuti vadzokere kunyika yeVaFirisitia. VaFirisitia ndokukwira kuJezireeri\x + 29.1. 2 Sam. 4.4.\x*.